agent.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    listAllAgents:
      path: /api/v1/agents
      method: GET
      auth:
        - JWTBearer: []
      docs: List all agents
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: List All Agents
      response:
        docs: Successful Response
        type: unknown
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - headers:
            X_SUPERAGENT_API_KEY: '[object Object]'
          response:
            body:
              key: value
    createAgent:
      path: /api/v1/agents
      method: POST
      auth:
        - JWTBearer: []
      docs: Create a new agent
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Create Agent
      request:
        name: Agent
        body:
          properties:
            name: string
            type: string
            llm:
              type: optional<map<string, unknown>>
            has_memory:
              type: optional<boolean>
              default: false
            documentId:
              type: optional<string>
            promptId:
              type: optional<string>
            toolId:
              type: optional<string>
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Successful Response
        type: unknown
        status-code: 200
      errors:
        - root.UnprocessableEntityError
      examples:
        - headers:
            X_SUPERAGENT_API_KEY: '[object Object]'
          request:
            name: name
            type: type
          response:
            body:
              key: value
    getAgent:
      path: /api/v1/agents/{agentId}
      method: GET
      auth:
        - JWTBearer: []
      docs: Get a specific agent
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      path-parameters:
        agentId: string
      display-name: Get Agent
      response:
        docs: Successful Response
        type: unknown
        status-code: 200
      errors:
        - root.UnprocessableEntityError
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            agentId: agentId
          headers:
            X_SUPERAGENT_API_KEY: '[object Object]'
          response:
            body:
              key: value
    deleteAgent:
      path: /api/v1/agents/{agentId}
      method: DELETE
      auth:
        - JWTBearer: []
      docs: Delete a specific agent
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      path-parameters:
        agentId: string
      display-name: Delete Agent
      response:
        docs: Successful Response
        type: unknown
        status-code: 200
      errors:
        - root.UnprocessableEntityError
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            agentId: agentId
          headers:
            X_SUPERAGENT_API_KEY: '[object Object]'
          response:
            body:
              key: value
    patchAgent:
      path: /api/v1/agents/{agentId}
      method: PATCH
      auth:
        - JWTBearer: []
      docs: Patch a specific agent
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      path-parameters:
        agentId: string
      display-name: Patch Agent
      request:
        body:
          type: map<string, unknown>
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Successful Response
        type: unknown
        status-code: 200
      errors:
        - root.UnprocessableEntityError
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            agentId: agentId
          headers:
            X_SUPERAGENT_API_KEY: '[object Object]'
          request:
            key: value
          response:
            body:
              key: value
    promptAgent:
      path: /api/v1/agents/{agentId}/predict
      method: POST
      auth:
        - APIKeyHeader: []
      docs: Invoke a specific agent
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      path-parameters:
        agentId: string
      display-name: Prompt Agent
      request:
        name: PredictAgent
        body:
          properties:
            input:
              type: map<string, unknown>
            has_streaming:
              type: optional<boolean>
              default: false
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Successful Response
        type: unknown
        status-code: 200
      errors:
        - root.UnprocessableEntityError
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            agentId: agentId
          headers:
            X_SUPERAGENT_API_KEY: '[object Object]'
          request:
            input:
              key: value
          response:
            body:
              key: value
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
